[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "黑色羽翼　前篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那天的事情，我無法將它忘記。那一天，我明白了何謂正義。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「為了我們的王，將『願望』交出來吧！」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "奇怪的人們突然出現，然後大家的樣子慢慢變得詭異。但是，我卻什麼也辦不到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為我什麼都不會。還只是個小孩，又是個膽小鬼，也不像每次都幫助這個村莊的王子大人他們那樣厲害。光躲在暗處發抖就已經用盡全力了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「嗯？有誰在那裡嗎！？」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "奇怪的人們朝我這裡過來了。……已經完蛋了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這時候，一道黑影疾馳而來。「出來吧，亞森！」那個人這麼叫著，就有個東西像是燃起的火焰般出現了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "出現在那裡的是有著巨大的黑色羽翼、看起來像戴著面具的人。搞不好那不是人也說不定。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "奇怪的人們身體開始膨脹，然後一個接一個都脹破了。接著，從裡面出現的是帶著銳利爪牙又相貌猙獰的魔獸。而他們兩人就這樣被魔獸包圍了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好可怕，真的好可怕，我明明一直想要趕快把視線避開……但雙眼卻不聽使喚，使我就這麼盯著與魔獸對峙的他們。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "他們的樣子沒有任何一點害怕。不只不怕，還露出了自信的笑容，然後跳上天空，把魔獸射穿了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「讓我收下吧！」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我覺得自己的心已經被那份強大給奪去了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210138011, "title": "黑色羽翼　前篇"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "黑色羽翼　後篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "即使重要的人遇到了威脅，當時的我也只能躲在暗處發抖。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為我是小孩，因為我很弱小。因為我不是王子大人。滿腦子都是各種藉口，卻沒有絲毫想要挺身而出的念頭。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是，我看到了黑色外套的人與黑色羽翼的人……現在，我的體內深處似乎有一陣火焰燃起。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我想要和這些人一樣。其實我不想要用任何理由來找藉口欺騙自己。我不想要放棄。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "從體內燃起的，是即使渾身顫抖也讓我能站起來的勇氣。那是讓我能挺身反抗的強烈意志──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要有了這份意志，我感覺不論是哪裡我都能飛到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……那場事件，即便是過了十幾年的今天，我仍是無法忘懷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「爸爸這次又保護村莊了對不對！我長大以後也想變得像爸爸一樣！」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聽著兒子這麼說，我想起了那黑色的羽翼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那天，我明白了何謂正義，而它至今也在我體內燃燒著。並且在這之後的未來，一定也不會熄滅。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210138012, "title": "黑色羽翼　後篇"}]